{Project_1:[Project_1_Domain@@Project_1_Cloud Computing:
Created a micro-services based website (and application counterpart). Created our own container orchestration system (like Kubernetes) – which performs health checks, scale-up, scale-down, load-balancing. The application uses 20+ APIs, has been written in Node, and is deployed on AWS. 

]##Project_2:[Project_2_Domain@@Project_2_Big Data:
Using Hadoop, Spark, and machine learning algorithms to perform a ball-by-ball analysis of any given IPL match. The algorithm can predict the outcome of every ball, every over, and hence the outcome of every match.

]##Project_3:[Project_3_Domain@@Project_3_Data Analytics:
Using various machine learning models to help application developers navigate the android app store by predicting the rating their apps would get based on relevant attributes. A future use-case is to help Android application developers tweak their applications to further popularize their applications.

]##Project_4:[Project_4_Domain@@Project_4_Operating Systems:
Built our own FUSE (Filesystem in Userspace) file system, in C. Implemented system calls and data structures required for a file system. Supports operations like ls, cat, rm, mkdir, etc.]}

