{Internship_1:[Internship_1_Company@@Internship_1_Research Intern (June 2018 – August 2018): 
•Worked on “Swift Power-Aware Scheduling”, with the Cloud Computing and Big Data Lab, PES University, Bangalore - aimed at implementing green technology in OpenStack’s object store.
