]##Internship_2:[Internship_2_Company@@Internship_2_Data Science, ML, and DL intern, NTT Data Services (June 2019 – Present):
•Worked on health insurance claim data, involving feature engineering and model creation to predict the exact reason for denial of certain insurance claims. Built a few machine learning models, whose parameters got used to further research after my internship period, as they performed well. Also built a neural network using Keras.

]##Internship_3:[Internship_3_Company@@Internship_3_Research Project (May 2019 – Present):
•Using computer vision and natural language processing to build more efficient recommendations on dating applications and websites, trying to match by interests and features of pictures. 
]##Internship_4:[Internship_4_Company@@Internship_4_Successfully built a data extraction/cleaning pipeline, implemented Stanford’s CSAIL model for scene understanding. Built word vectors using fasttext, and character-level models.
